| Trivia                  = * Lt. Col. Louis compares Captain America to the DC Comics hero [[w:c:dc:Superman|Superman]] when Dr. Vaselli transforms Steve Rogers into the super soldier.
* The young Tom Kimball and Sam Kolawetz wonder if the person Tom saw strapped to the Red Skull's rocket could have been the [[Namor|Sub-Mariner]] or the [[Jim Hammond|Human Torch]]. Sam suggests they should use their [[wikipedia:Captain Midnight|Captain Midnight]] decoder ring.
